# === Claude Code ===
# Ignore everything under .claude/ EXCEPT skills/ — those are project code, not local state.
# (Plain `.claude/` would un-includably blanket-ignore the whole tree; using `.claude/*`
# lets the negation rule below re-include a specific subdirectory.)
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md

# === Unclassified — origin TBD, monitoring ===
.cache/
.env*.local
